                    },
                    "body": "Scheduling for 1.5.1. \n\nOne note: I think that init() should be called not as the *last* item in __construct(), but the last item before the call to loadDefaultDecorators(). This would allow you to prevent the default decorators from loading if you were to create them in your init() method.",
